sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant T as Telegram API
    participant n8n
    participant E as Email (Gmail / Outlook)
    participant AI as AI (Basic LLM Chain)

    %% Workflow 3 (Gmail) / Workflow 4 (Outlook)

    E->>n8n: Email Trigger: new unread email

    par Classification and label/folder list in parallel
        n8n->>AI: Basic LLM Chain: subject + preview
        AI-->>n8n: category (e.g. "n8n/newsletter")
    and
        n8n->>E: Get Many Labels (Gmail) / Get Many Folders (Outlook)
        E-->>n8n: label/folder list with IDs
    end

    n8n->>n8n: Merge: combine category + list
    n8n->>n8n: Code: find label/folder ID by name

    alt Gmail
        n8n->>E: Gmail: Add Label (label ID)
    else Outlook
        n8n->>E: Outlook: Move Message (folder ID)
    end

    alt Urgent email
        n8n->>T: Telegram: urgent email notification (fixed Chat ID)
        T-->>U: 🚨 Urgent email from: ...
    end
